{
  "stem": "2118.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The delousing barracks, which means you weren't-- disaffecting barracks and the shower barracks, were also burned out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So when we came, and we came at night, it looked like a [NON-ENGLISH], like hell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he-- they drove us on that line in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And here was coal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was coal for the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Maybe-- I don't know how many hundreds of yards stacked up with coal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the whole pile was burning, like a big fire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And there were burned out wagons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they took us down, and they led us into a barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the people who came to take us down-- was all at night-- to take us down wearing the striped suits.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they had dogs, big dogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And those were kapos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they controlled us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "You know, we're 580 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It was hard to control.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We were thirsty and hungry and tired and all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "This was the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And here was this square chimney belching fire-- not smoke, but fire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And the smell-- it was a smell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "This was the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And the smell was terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And in the morning, we saw already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "So they made us undress.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we stood outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We undressed outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "We put all-- all our clothing in a package and laid it down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I took my mother's ring, and I put it in a piece of soap.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I squeezed it in and I took it with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Of course, this was silly too, because if not for the that fire I would have never seen the soap or the clothing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Now, what happens is that the fire burned their store rooms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And they had no striped suits to give us out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "So a guy came.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
